{"id":190072,"type":1,"name":"ちび☆デビ!","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/a2/bb/190072_nJjUg.jpg","summary":"　　一個從小失去父母，在學校老是被欺負的國中女生－澤田帆乃香，某天早上醒來居然發現自己床上躺了一個小嬰兒，伴隨而來卻是一連串的災難。神祕二人組無所不用其極地想搶走小嬰兒。而自稱是小惡魔托兒所的園長，更是讓人摸不著頭緒。但這個小嬰兒不是普通人，而是擁有特殊能力的惡魔之子。平凡的帆乃香也因此展開了一段不可思議的全新生活。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>魔法小恶魔</li><li><span>册数: </span>11</li><li><span>话数: </span>79</li><li><span>作者: </span><a href=\"/person/1503\">篠塚ひろむ</a></li><li><span>出版社: </span><a href=\"/person/6749\">小学館</a>、<a href=\"/person/7033\">東立出版社</a>、<a href=\"/person/7613\">玉皇朝</a></li><li><span>连载杂志: </span><a href=\"/person/7792\">ちゃお</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>魔法小惡魔</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>恶魔宝宝</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>惡魔寶寶</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Chibi☆Devil</li><li><span>开始: </span>2008-05-01(2008年6月号)</li><li><span>结束: </span>2014-11-01(2014年12月号)</li>","collection":{"collect":1},"tags":[{"name":"全11卷","count":1},{"name":"已完结","count":1},{"name":"漫画系列","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":1503,"image":"","name":"筱冢广梦","desc":"作者"},{"id":7613,"image":"","name":"玉皇朝","desc":"出版社"},{"id":6749,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/2c/ec/6749_prsn_O9b2I.jpg","name":"小学馆","desc":"出版社"},{"id":7033,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/fd/24/7033_prsn_J3N83.jpg","name":"东立出版社","desc":"出版社"},{"id":7792,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/fa/91/7792_prsn_XiQHu.jpg","name":"ちゃお","desc":"连载杂志"}],"relations":[{"id":22849,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/b1/cc/22849_vdj2i.jpg","title":"ちび☆デビ!","type":"动画","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/22849"}],"comic":[{"id":190073,"name":"ちび☆デビ! (1)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/f4/7e/190073_jp.jpg"},{"id":190074,"name":"ちび☆デビ! (2)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/6c/af/190074_jp.jpg"},{"id":190075,"name":"ちび☆デビ! (3)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/10/12/190075_jp.jpg"},{"id":190076,"name":"ちび☆デビ! (4)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/6f/d6/190076_jp.jpg"},{"id":190077,"name":"ちび☆デビ! (5)","image"